creator: TheFrenchSoftware
descriptionHtml:
Everywhere,
- Show on your camera in augmented reality the islands near the coast.
- Knows position, height and distance of few 200.000 islands worldwide.
- Works device offline.

when device online,
- Show islands on a auto-rotate 3D map near you location in topographic rendering.
- Give access to the photos of each selected islands.
descriptionShort: Discover the names of islands and emerged lands around you in augmented reality.
title: Island Finder AR
